lished on<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">dt</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">dd</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text-base font-medium leading-6 text-gray-500&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">time</span> <span class="hljs-attr">datetime</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;2023-04-24T16:24:00.000Z&quot;</span>&gt;</span>April 24, 2023<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">time</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">dd</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">dl</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;xl:col-span-3&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h3</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text-xl font-bold leading-8 text-gray-900&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">href</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hover:underline&quot;</span>&gt;</span>如何使用 GitHub Actions 自动化部署<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h3</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text-base font-medium leading-6 text-gray-500&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><br>            GitHub Actions 是 GitHub 提供的一项自动化工具，可以帮助开发者更方便地进行持续集成和持续部署。本文介绍如何使用 GitHub Actions 实现自动化部署。<br>          <span class